## Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Build the plugin
nx build <%= projectName %>

# Pack the plugin for distribution
nx pack <%= projectName %>
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { pluginName } from '@<%= npmScope %>/<%= projectName %>';

console.log(pluginName()); // <%= projectName %>
```

